---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Your Name - Portfolio">
  <section class="space-y-6">
    <div class="text-center space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Hi, I'm Sarthak</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        Software Engineer with a focus on Platform and Infrastructure
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p>
        Welcome to my corner of the web! I'm a Software Engineer interested in solving Platform and Infrastructure problems. I have extensive experience working with AWS Cloud services like S3, EC2, ECS, EKS, SNS, SQS, AWS Networking, EBS, ElastiCache, CloudWatch, RDS, and more. I am also skilled in message broker systems like Kafka, databases such as MongoDB, Postgres, and MySQL, and workflow orchestration tools like Temporal.
      </p>
      <p>
        I was one of the founding contributors to Vedantu's in-house video engine powering their live classes and the sole developer responsible for building their VQuiz product backend from the ground up!
      </p>
      <p>
        Proficient in TypeScript, Go, and Java, I have developed complete systems impacting millions of lives. I am always eager to learn new technologies to solve the challenges your company might be facing.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-12">
      <div class="p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Skills</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>AWS Cloud Services</li>
          <li>Message Broker Systems</li>
          <li>Database Management</li>
          <li>Workflow Orchestration</li>
          <li>TypeScript, Go, Java</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Featured Projects</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>
            <a href="https://tech.vedantu.com/works/inhouse-video-streaming/" class="text-primary hover:underline">How we built our own in-house Video Streaming Platform?</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.vedantu.com/vquiz" class="text-primary hover:underline">VQuiz Product Backend</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/TypicalDefender/entangleDB" class="text-primary hover:underline">EntangleDB</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>